stories.text:
Triangulating feedback is a great way to get the honest truth about your product.

It's hard to find and schedule time with constructive people that will listen and talk about what you're building.

I made this room on Vibehut (1-on-1 video) to let anyone jump on and show off what they've been working on or give feedback. You can share your screen and record your calls for review / posting to socials.

Join this Room: https://vibehut.io/rooms/62057f07677a4500163737d5

Password to start call: grow3

The room is open 24/7, I've also added in a few event times for everyone to join.
